{"tid":528193,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 改口承認其處理器會受 Spectre 漏洞影響","createTime":"2018-01-13T13:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T19:25:53.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"036b3969a35a38e96fd3c30e7389111c70d86efb","tid":528193,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/13/amd-spectre/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2Famd-spectre%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=O%2BsyYLFTxwcZnUDajpZneWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=522eccd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/13/amd-spectre/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前 AMD 才宣稱最近被發現的 Meltdown 與 Spectre 漏洞對他們的處理器沒有影響，但他們在美國時間前日 (11日) 發表聲明，指「Spectre」漏洞雖然極難於搭載 AMD 處理器的系統內應用，但電腦有可能會被該漏洞的兩款變種攻擊。為以防萬一，AMD 將會為 Windows 與 Linux 提供系統更新，最快會於數日內向 OS 生產商提供。而另一款 Meltdown 漏洞則不存在於所有 AMD 處理器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/l_yu_amd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fl_yu_amd1.jpg&h=a2344f27&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"795de41b60e4f21f405649435854a4b6de335e25","tid":528193,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"美國 AMD 在美國時間 11 日公佈了關於「Spectre」處理器漏洞的對應方案。他們會在數日內為 Ryzen 以及 EPYC 處理器提供更新檔案，向合作企業、OS 生產商提供。而一般用戶就要等候 Windows、Linux 提供系統更新。<br />\n<br />\n公佈當中亦提及了早前微軟的系統更新中，令到一部份搭載有 AMD 舊型處理器 Opteron、Athlon、Turion X2 的部份系統出現「變磚」不能啟動的情況。AMD 指會同微軟合作，在數日內提供系統更新。<br />\n<br />\nAMD 指出，最近被學者公佈的另一個「Meltdown」漏洞對他們的處理器毫無影響，另一方面 AMD 的 GPU「Radeon」系列則不受任何漏洞所影響。"},{"pid":"0186f647844f5fcfe10ba54bdbb600ab4ca0bbe6","tid":528193,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聲明原文: <a href=\"http://www.amd.com/en/corporate/speculative-execution\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amd.com%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Fspeculative-execution&d=O%2BsyYLFTxwcZnUDajpZneWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ac3ed1cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.amd.com/en/corporate/speculative-execution</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/snap4815-768x568.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fsnap4815-768x568.png&h=5e5fc145&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"228a3378b63f3cccb28ed25878e2250a0e509956","tid":528193,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T18:34:39.000Z","msg":"機會低好多"},{"pid":"e901066f40a3d62d88acc078066b057b7a48c159","tid":528193,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:17:32.000Z","msg":"冇性能影響同你平時Windows更新修復bugs有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50c01cd21bd57827162ca2bb13cc1387b860f8b","tid":528193,"uid":73728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:25:53.000Z","msg":"起碼叫親口認"}]}